The deadline for devel Bioconductor 3.20 packages to pass R CMD build and R CMD check is October 25th.  While you will still be able to make commits past this date,  This ensures any changes pushed to git.bioconductor.org are reflected in at least one build report before the devel branch will be copied to a release 3.20 branch.  We will freeze and create the 3.20 branch officially on October 29 in preparation for the October 30th release.

